Unpopular Opinion: Ariana Grande ain't shit.

You don't just walk away completely from something you're tied to because you feel overwhelmed. If that was gonna be the case, shoulda swerved from the start; you knew what type of dude he was.

I get it might have been toxic for her, but imagine getting engaged to a comedian you barely know because you wanted the publicity to smack your ex in the face so he could get his shit together. And then imagine overdosing on painkillers because you had to watch your ex do that shit knowing full well you were more of a husband than anyone else she could be with. She was playing with lives like that. I may be bitter, but she deserves no peace.
